1
00:00:22,850 --> 00:00:29,850
♪Our tangled destiny
has trapped my heart in this life♪

2
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:36,060
♪Will I see you again in the next life♪

3
00:00:36,550 --> 00:00:43,500
♪Keep a piece of peach blossom
to remember the past and say goodbye♪

4
00:00:43,830 --> 00:00:49,920
♪But I still miss you
with tears in my eyes♪

5
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:57,250
♪Dig a hole, plant a tree, but the leaves
and flowers remind me of our past♪

6
00:00:57,480 --> 00:01:03,710
♪Sow the seeds of love,
but they bloom on the wrong path♪

7
00:01:04,340 --> 00:01:11,060
♪Move on, let go,
forget everything about you♪

8
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:18,220
♪Flowers fall on the road
where I fell in love with you♪

9
00:01:33,020 --> 00:01:37,660
=Stolen Love=

10
00:01:37,860 --> 00:01:40,700
=Episode 30=

11
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:41,960
Get the cage!

12
00:01:42,320 --> 00:01:43,160
Mother, no!

13
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:46,400
Mother!

14
00:01:48,080 --> 00:01:49,680
I'm willing to quit my job

15
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:51,680
and assist Yanru.

16
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:54,240
Mother, please have mercy on her!

17
00:01:57,640 --> 00:02:00,480
His Majesty made you the Grand Tutor,

18
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:03,160
and both His Highness
and His Majesty trust you.

19
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:05,800
You defied the court
and betrayed our family.

20
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:09,120
I won't allow her to ruin you!

21
00:02:09,640 --> 00:02:10,480
Take her away!

22
00:02:11,640 --> 00:02:12,680
How dare you?

23
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:15,120
Mother, if you insist,

24
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:18,840
I'll have to cut my flesh!

25
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:23,400
What's all the fuss about?

26
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:31,440
Greetings, Your Highness.

27
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:34,520
Sorry, I didn't know you were back.

28
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:36,680
Aunt, you're too polite.

29
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:40,360
I was busy arresting some merchants
involved in the case.

30
00:02:41,880 --> 00:02:43,080
Now that it's finished,

31
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:44,560
I'm here to visit you.

32
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:51,720
Why are you punishing her

33
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:52,920
like this?

34
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:56,200
Your Highness, she committed adultery!

35
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:57,320
How dare you?

36
00:02:58,200 --> 00:02:59,400
You said she committed adultery.

37
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,360
Who's the other side?

38
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:02,640
Is it my fiance Xiao Chuyi?

39
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:06,720
Are you humiliating the royal family?

40
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,440
Your Highness, mercy.

41
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:15,660
Allow me...

42
00:03:15,670 --> 00:03:17,400
I don't want to waste time on you.

43
00:03:17,910 --> 00:03:19,400
You can kill her.

44
00:03:19,530 --> 00:03:21,370
However, if I become
the joke of the city,

45
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,920
no matter how powerful you are,

46
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:26,520
I'll eliminate all of you.

47
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:33,800
Lady Lu and the Prince Consort...

48
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:39,560
Nothing happened.

49
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,000
Release her!

50
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:46,640
Yunxi.

51
00:03:49,200 --> 00:03:51,200
Your Highness,
thank you for saving my life.

52
00:03:51,760 --> 00:03:52,600
No need.

53
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:53,720
You should thank

54
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,560
your ex-husband.

55
00:04:01,610 --> 00:04:03,980
You risked your life for her again.

56
00:04:04,660 --> 00:04:06,520
Lady Zhou is so vicious.

57
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,680
Yun is in trouble.

58
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:11,520
Only you can save her.

59
00:04:12,410 --> 00:04:14,080
You want to eliminate the Zhou Family.

60
00:04:14,540 --> 00:04:16,410
If she becomes the lady in charge,

61
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:18,040
you'll never get back together.

62
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:19,160
Why are you helping her?

63
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:23,720
She's always wanted to be
the lady in charge.

64
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,640
I don't want it,

65
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,400
but I can't watch her fail
because of me.

66
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,000
Okay.

67
00:04:32,440 --> 00:04:33,280
I'll do it,

68
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:35,120
but you must promise me one thing.

69
00:04:37,380 --> 00:04:39,960
When Lu Yunxi
becomes the lady in charge,

70
00:04:40,510 --> 00:04:42,280
you'll leave the capital with me.

71
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:46,880
I can't.

72
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:50,200
I haven't got revenge on the Zhous
and the Crown Prince.

73
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,610
I can't leave at this crucial time.

74
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:55,400
You said you'd help me
avoid the royal marriage.

75
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,600
If you die,

76
00:04:57,600 --> 00:05:00,120
I'll have to marry the retard
from Chen Kingdom!

77
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:02,600
Are you going to break your promise?

78
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:05,240
It's not up to you.

79
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:06,560
If you reject me,

80
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,400
I won't save her.

81
00:05:07,880 --> 00:05:08,720
Liuyun.

82
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:23,720
Never mind.

83
00:05:26,810 --> 00:05:28,050
I promise you

84
00:05:30,610 --> 00:05:31,920
if you save Yun,

85
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:36,000
I'll do anything for you.

86
00:05:49,540 --> 00:05:51,540
(Zhou's Mansion)

87
00:05:51,540 --> 00:05:54,180
(The Ancestral Worship Ceremony)

88
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:12,720
Ancestors, please enjoy the tribute
and bless our family.

89
00:06:13,080 --> 00:06:15,680
May our family

90
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,840
rise and thrive.

91
