May our family

94
00:06:27,640 --> 00:06:29,920
rise and thrive.

95
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,880
My Lady, please wait a minute.

96
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:51,320
Since all our family are here,

97
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:54,400
I want to have a discussion with you.

98
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,520
Go ahead.

99
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:59,160
Lord Zhou has gained a foothold
in the court,

100
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:02,840
but you're still managing
the family affairs on your own.

101
00:07:03,060 --> 00:07:05,620
Many people have complained about this.

102
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:08,080
Yanyu is busy with work.

103
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:09,720
As his mother,

104
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:12,590
I'm obliged to relieve his burden.

105
00:07:14,210 --> 00:07:16,360
Every mother loves their children.

106
00:07:16,780 --> 00:07:18,440
I understand.

107
00:07:18,690 --> 00:07:21,200
However, things shouldn't
get out of control,

108
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:22,720
or it'll be a disaster.

109
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:27,320
Why don't you hand over
the family business to Lady Lu

110
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:30,720
so that you can live a peaceful life
in your later years?

111
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,440
Yanyu,

112
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:49,400
what's your opinion?

113
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:53,560
It's our duty

114
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:55,280
to relieve your burden.

115
00:07:58,810 --> 00:08:02,100
Wish Lady Zhou happiness

116
00:08:02,100 --> 00:08:04,000
and longevity.

117
