Wish Lady Zhou happiness

118
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:12,320
and longevity.

119
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:19,320
I've really underestimated you.

120
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:22,600
When did you steal my power?

121
00:08:28,530 --> 00:08:29,410
Mother,

122
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:32,320
thank you for your trust.

123
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:34,640
- You...
- As the lady in charge,

124
00:08:35,280 --> 00:08:36,800
I must make contributions

125
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,640
so as to repay your kindness

126
00:08:38,920 --> 00:08:40,320
and make our family thrive.

127
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,560
Good.

128
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:53,160
Wonderful!

129
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:56,240
In that case,

130
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:59,600
please leave us alone.

131
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:05,450
I have something to hand over
to the new lady in charge.

132
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,360
Look carefully.

133
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:32,400
I won't do it again.

134
00:10:15,520 --> 00:10:19,560
Aren't you afraid
that I'll kill you here?

135
00:10:19,860 --> 00:10:21,720
Mother, if you kill me,

136
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:24,840
how are you going to
explain it to them,

137
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:26,920
and what will people say about this,

138
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:29,160
about you and our family?

139
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:32,640
Don't think you can
control the Zhou family

140
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:34,280
with these lickspittles' support.

141
00:10:34,920 --> 00:10:36,880
As long as I'm alive.

142
00:10:37,770 --> 00:10:41,440
I'll always be in charge of
our family business.

143
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,280
What are you doing?

144
00:10:52,560 --> 00:10:53,960
Control the family

145
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,280
and obtain the treasures? So what?

146
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:57,910
I only want the scroll.

147
00:10:58,760 --> 00:11:00,120
The rest of them

148
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:02,560
will be your grave goods.

149
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,040
My Lady! My Lady!

150
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:26,720
My Lady, what are you doing?

151
00:11:30,580 --> 00:11:32,140
(Zhou Family Ancestral Hall)

152
00:11:42,920 --> 00:11:43,880
Lu Yunxi,

153
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:45,720
you betrayed us.

154
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:49,650
You promised to keep the secret

155
00:11:49,650 --> 00:11:50,760
when you got the position.

156
00:11:51,040 --> 00:11:52,760
How can you betray us

157
00:11:52,760 --> 00:11:54,080
now?

158
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:56,400
Are you going to destroy all of us?

159
00:11:56,400 --> 00:11:58,000
- Exactly!
- Yes!

160
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,680
God knows everything.

161
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:02,520
Your hands have been stained with blood.

162
00:12:03,760 --> 00:12:06,280
You've committed so many crimes.

163
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:08,560
Shouldn't you pay the price?

164
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:13,040
Lu Yunxi,

165
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:16,160
you've been here for seven years,

166
00:12:16,560 --> 00:12:19,160
and the only thing
you've ever wanted is revenge.

167
00:12:22,880 --> 00:12:24,720
Idiots!

168
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:27,280
How dare you betray me?
Go to hell!

169
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,920
The Zhou Family
can't protect you anymore.

170
00:12:30,330 --> 00:12:32,400
Even His Highness can't save you!

171
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,040
You...

172
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:41,680
Do you know what she's holding?

173
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:52,160
It's the alliance letter
between the Crown Prince and Wujiang.

174
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:55,760
The Crown Prince is a traitor?
Impossible.

175
00:12:55,760 --> 00:12:57,040
How's that possible?

176
00:12:58,680 --> 00:12:59,720
Seven years ago,

177
00:13:00,750 --> 00:13:03,880
Prince Su led 30 thousand great soldiers
to attack Wujiang,

178
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:06,560
but they were ambushed
by 100 thousand soldiers

179
00:13:07,240 --> 00:13:08,280
and trapped in Luoxia Ridge.

180
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:11,200
How... How's that possible?

181
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,320
I can't believe it.

182
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:14,800
Everyone thought Prince Su
fell for their trap,

183
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:20,400
but it was the Crown Prince
who leaked our information to Wujiang

184
00:13:20,920 --> 00:13:22,600
and formed an alliance with them.

185
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:25,760
How did she know?

186
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:29,840
Witnessed by blood,

187
00:13:30,650 --> 00:13:32,440
I'll form an eternal alliance
with Wujiang.

188
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:34,440
When I take the throne,

189
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:37,840
I'll give Wujiang thousands of
acres of land as rewards.

190
00:13:42,380 --> 00:13:46,900
(Xiao Wan'er)

191
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:51,840
Wait.

192
00:13:55,340 --> 00:13:58,980
(Prince Luesha of Wujiang)

193
00:13:59,560 --> 00:14:01,840
Your Highness, My Lady, don't worry.

194
00:14:03,640 --> 00:14:04,960
Prince Su and Xiao Chuyi

195
00:14:05,830 --> 00:14:07,250
will no longer exist in this world

196
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,760
after the battle of Luoxia Ridge.

197
00:14:19,060 --> 00:14:21,140
(Defense Map)

198
00:14:27,920 --> 00:14:28,920
Let's go.

199
00:14:38,440 --> 00:14:39,440
Your Highness.

200
00:14:39,800 --> 00:14:41,800
It can't be placed
in the Eastern Palace.

201
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:47,520
Keep it in your secret room.

202
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:50,040
Okay.

203
00:15:00,080 --> 00:15:00,960
This...

204
00:15:01,160 --> 00:15:02,280
How's that possible?

205
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:05,400
Treason

206
00:15:05,640 --> 00:15:06,840
and murder.

207
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:08,550
That the Crown Prince you chose

208
00:15:08,740 --> 00:15:10,120
and the Zhou Family you count on!

209
00:15:10,560 --> 00:15:11,600
It's impossible.

210
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:14,880
My Lady!

211
00:15:14,880 --> 00:15:16,680
- My Lady!
- My Lady!

212
00:15:17,040 --> 00:15:18,200
I'm going to die anyway.

213
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:20,000
I'll kill you!

214
00:15:21,640 --> 00:15:24,040
General Xiao ordered me
to protect Lady Lu!

215
00:15:29,120 --> 00:15:31,360
No wonder Chuyi loves you so much.

216
00:15:33,880 --> 00:15:34,880
Lu Yunxi.

217
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:37,400
Give me the scroll.

218
00:15:42,400 --> 00:15:44,440
I'll report it to my father
and investigate it.

219
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:51,960
The Xiaos never embezzled
the military rations.

220
00:15:52,720 --> 00:15:54,680
Your Highness, please report it
to His Majesty

221
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:56,480
and clear their names.

222
00:15:57,400 --> 00:15:58,240
I promise you

223
00:15:58,760 --> 00:16:00,320
I'll bring justice to you,

224
00:16:00,320 --> 00:16:01,840
the Xiaos, and the world.

225
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:03,780
Brother, wait.

226
